1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs the creation,
 maintenance,
 verification,
 and retirement of Configuration Item (CI) records for all deployed IT assets within the Elko County Information Operations Department (ECIO).
\end_layout

